<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Author. (Year of publication). <em>Title of report</em> (Report No). 
	Name of Government Department if not the author. Retrieved from URL.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Examples</strong>
<br>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Author">Department of Health and Ageing</span>. 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2008</span>). 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of report">Ageing and aged care in Australia</span></em> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Report No.">Publication No. P3&#45;4147</span>). 
